

'''= a 'labelprinter/tracking system', i.e. a tool to link Objects and projects in a space to individual wiki pages'''


URL = https://labitat.dk/wiki/Labitrack [https://github.com/labitat/labitrack]

=Description=

"Labitrack, created for the Labitat hackerspace: A small python app generates stickers containing human readable text, icons and a QR code. Objects and projects in the space are linked to individual wiki pages containing a template with key-value pairs. Any tagged item in the space can be scanned for more info such as: Where does the item belong (for easy cleanup by newcomers), link to manual/specs, contact info for people responsible / willing to teach how to use item. This system is currently in use in the Labitat space."
(http://newschallenge2.tumblr.com/post/25571859265/mycelia-a-community-asset-mapping-autodocumentation)

